Subsequent to December 31, 2019, we made net repayments of $600.0 million under the 2019 Credit Facility, including
repayments of approximately $1,483.4 million using the proceeds from our issuance of the 2.400% Notes and 2.900% Notes (each
as defined below), and made net borrowings of $271.8 million under the 2019 Multicurrency Credit Facility. The borrowings were
used to repay existing indebtedness and for general corporate purposes.
